title: UltimateSurrender--US-30897 Darling and Izamar Gutierrez WMV
description:

WMV only. MP4 + Pics later.

"The Grappler"

Izamar Gutierrez

Weight:  130lbs

Two fan Favorites use the old US mat for the very Last match ever in the old mat room. We wouldn't want it any other way.

We are getting deeper and deeper into the Summer Vengeance Tournament which means the competition is getting better and better. Today we put two highly skilled grapplers on the mats together. Darling has been wrestling for U/S since season 3. She is ranked 5th in the tournament. Izamar is ranked 4th just above her. She may be new to U/S as of last season but she has about 12 years of wrestling experience and is the current Welter Weight Champion. These two have never met on the U/S mats. The favorite to win is Izamar Gutierrez but we have had a few surprises this season. Darling may cause an upset. 

Loser gets fucked hard and fast with some embarrassing verbal humiliation.
